    • addHasTags

      public void addHasTags(String text)
      Adds hashtags from given text to the list of hashtags in the capsule. Hashtags must be in the format #hashtag#, and will be extracted and added without the # characters.
      Parameters:
      text - the text to extract hashtags from

    • createCapsuleURL

      public String createCapsuleURL()

      Returns:
      the URL for the capsule

    • createCapsuleHTML

      public void createCapsuleHTML()
      Creates an HTML file for the capsule containing all the information about it. The file will be saved in a "capsulesHTML" directory in the project directory.

    • matchQueryWithHastag

      public boolean matchQueryWithHastag(String query)
      Determines if the given query matches any of the hashtags in the list of hashtags.
      Parameters:
      query - the query to match against hashtags
      Returns:
      true if the query matches any of the hashtags, false otherwise
